robowars
Class Bullet

java.lang.Object
  robowars.Bullet
public final class Bullet
extends java.lang.Object

The Bullet class is instantiated when a robot fires. Bullets can be fired with a power in the range 1 - 3. Higher the power of the bullet, lower the velocity of the bullet, higher the gun heat and higher the damage caused to the opponent.

The conventions regarding axis and angles are the same as in Robot.
